        },
        {
            type: "song",
            text: "There's a lotta little things you've gotta do in this world!",
            href: "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3vuzWBB8ETY",
        },
        {
            type: "song",
            text: "'Cause rainbows won't light up the sky, unless you let it rain!",
            href: "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RAhqxvgQYn0",
        },
        {
            type: "song",
            text: "You're in my head like a catchy song!",
